cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the development of a new generation of routing platforms that use SDN controllers to automate and optimize network configuration. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of optimization and machine learning algorithms to control networks in real-time. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper discusses the design of a new control plane architecture for routing systems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of machine learning algorithms for network optimization. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of SDN controllers for network automation and optimization.
